File Sharing System API

OAS 3.0

H thng chia s file tm thi vi cc tnh nng:

  • Upload file v to link chia s
  • Thit lp quyn truy cp (public/password-protected/private)
  • Thi gian hiu lc linh hot (from/to)
  • Bo v bng mt khu hoc TOTP
  • Chia s vi danh sch ngi dng c th
  • T ng xa file ht hn

Authentication

User authentication and authorization

To ti khon ngi dng mi (khng bt buc upload file).

Lu :

  • User t ng k s lun c role = user (mc nh)
  • Admin account c to qua script/seed data hoc endpoint ring (ch admin gi c)

Lu v TOTP/2FA:

  • Khng th bt TOTP ngay khi ng k
  • Sau khi ng k, user cn ng nhp ly Bearer token
  • Sau gi /auth/totp/setup v /auth/totp/verify bt 2FA

Files

File management operations

Upload file mi v to share link. Authorization header l optional - nu khng c th anonymous upload (ch upload c file public).

Lu :

  • Cc cu hnh private (isPublic = false, dng whitelist sharedWith, password nng cao) yu cu Bearer token h thng gn owner.
  • Anonymous upload lun isPublic = true v khng th chnh sa/xa file sau khi upload.
  • Thi gian hiu lc c validate theo system policy: availableFrom phi nh hn hoc bng availableTo, availableTo khng c nm trong qu kh v tng thi gian hiu lc khng vt qu maxValidityDays. Nu b trng, backend t p dng logic mc nh (FROM+TO/Ch FROM/Ch TO/Khng c) nh m t phn Validity Period.

Parameters

No parameters

Request body

file *
string($binary)

File cn upload

isPublic
boolean

File public hay private (upload n danh lun = true)

password
string

Mt khu bo v (min 8 k t)

availableFrom
string($date-time)

Thi im bt u hiu lc (khng c ln hn availableTo v khng vt qu khong thi gian cho php trong system_policy.maxValidityDays).

Mc nh: Nu c availableFrom v availableTo u null, h thng t ng set:

  • availableFrom = thi im hin ti
  • availableTo = thi im hin ti + 7 ngy (default_validity_days)
availableTo
string($date-time)

Thi im kt thc hiu lc (khng nm trong qu kh, phi ln hn availableFrom v nh hn gii hn maxValidityDays).

Mc nh: Nu c availableFrom v availableTo u null, h thng t ng set:

  • availableFrom = thi im hin ti
  • availableTo = thi im hin ti + 7 ngy (default_validity_days)
sharedWith
array<string>

Ly download history t bng download_history (tng t browser download history).

Yu cu: Ch owner hoc admin mi xem c

Thng tin mi download:

  • Ngi download (username/email hoc "Anonymous")
  • Thi im download
  • Trng thi (completed/interrupted)

Quyn ring t:

  • Vi anonymous download, h thng ch ghi nhn mt bn ghi mang nhn "Anonymous" cng timestamp v trng thi; khng log IP/User-Agent hoc fingerprint.
  • Thng tin c nhn (username/email) ch xut hin khi ngi ti ng nhp v ng vi iu khon s dng.

Download file. File c th c nhiu lp bo mt cng lc (password + whitelist).

Th t kim tra bo mt (theo best practice):

  1. File status - Kim tra file cn hiu lc (expired/pending) 410/423
  2. Whitelist - Nu file c sharedWith list yu cu Bearer token, verify user email whitelist 403 nu khng c quyn
  3. Password - Nu file c password yu cu header X-File-Password 403 nu sai/thiu

Lu : Tt c cc lp bo mt phi pass th mi c download. Bt k lp no fail s tr error tng ng.

Owner preview trong giai on pending:

  • Nu requester l owner (JWT hp l, sub trng file.owner.id), h thng cho php bypass trng thi pending ch file c th kim th trc khi ti gi.
  • Tt c user khc vn nhn 423 "File not yet available" cho ti khi availableFrom n.

Notification khi file chuyn trng thi:

  • Khuyn ngh cu hnh cronjob/background task gi email/SMS/webhook khi file chuyn t pending sang active owner v whitelist nhn thng bo.
  • Endpoint ny khng t gi notification; cn bt tnh nng backend hoc job scheduler (xem mc Appendices/Future Enhancements).

Admin

Admin-only operations

Xa file ht hn (Cron job hoc Admin endpoint). Yu cu X-Cron-Secret header hoc admin token.

Security best practices:

  • X-Cron-Secret phi c lu trong mi trng bo mt, h tr rotation nh k (v d i secret hng tun/thng).
  • Nn trin khai rate limiting/IP allowlist trnh b spam cleanup (DOS).
  • Mi request ti endpoint ny cn c log y (timestamp, source, kt qu) audit.
  • Khuyn ngh trin khai song song xc thc bng JWT admin i vi cc tc v th cng; secret ch yu dnh cho job ni b.
